data.description: Experience luxury living in this exquisite one-year young home nestled on a sprawling 0.85-acre lot. From the moment you step into the impressive 2-story foyer, you'll be enchanted by the grandeur this residence offers. The great room, adorned with a cozy fireplace, seamlessly flows into the extra-large kitchen, complete with a delightful keeping room and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Granite counters, a wall-oven, microwave, and dishwasher add a touch of sophistication. Perfect for entertaining, the kitchen island with a breakfast bar is a delightful gathering spot. Beyond the main living areas lies a separate living/office space, as well as a formal dining room boasting elegant, coffered ceilings. One guest suite is conveniently located on the main floor, providing privacy and comfort for your visitors. Upstairs, an opulent owner's suite awaits, featuring a cozy sitting area, an impressively spacious walk-in closet, a luxurious tub, a separate tile shower, dual vanities, and fine tile flooring. Three additional bedrooms and two baths ensure ample space for everyone. The upper level also boasts a large laundry room with a utility sink, offering practicality and convenience. For your leisure and entertainment, there's a versatile loft and a media room with a kitchen which can also be used as a man cave. Car enthusiasts will appreciate the three-car garage, while a fenced yard ensures privacy and security. Retreat outdoors to the covered extra-large screened-in patio, complete with a charming outdoor fireplace. Conveniently located a mere 20 minutes from Robins AFB, this exceptional property is an absolute must-see. Impeccably maintained and better than new, this home epitomizes elegance and luxury living. ***Assumable VA loan at 3.37% rate***
